::About
PyNetCCTV is a simple IP-camera CCTV package that displays live CCTV feeds and records snapshots.

THIS SOFTWARE IS STILL IN DEVELOPMENT AND NOT YET READY TO BE USED

However - you're welcome to download it, have a play and get in touch with comments and suggestions... ed@rameus.org.uk

